      "title": "Rosenlew",
      "score": 0.04220011234897233,
      "text": "Rosenlew\nElectrolux owns the brand in home appliances and uses it in Finland. Electrolux stopped the manufacturing of fridges in Pori, Finland, in 1998.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.049996251961699545,
